<p>
	This stunning looking candle is blended with quality essential oils to create a sweet and citrus top note with rich mandarin and orange fragranced flowers building up from an aromatic base of subtle spices. This candle will give you hours of burning time to enjoy the beautiful aroma. When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
